<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>最短ハート交換シミュレーション</title>
<meta name="description" content="連れ歩きとキャンドル購入をこの精霊に集中させた場合の、最短でハートと交換できるルート解説">
<link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>%E2%9D%A4%EF%B8%8F</text></svg>">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=M+PLUS+Rounded+1c:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #FFF7EC;
    --card: #FFFFFF;
    --ink: #4A3A2C;
    --muted: #8F7A62;
    --apricot: #FF9F45;
    --apricot-dark: #E17A1B;
    --apricot-pale: #FFEBD3;
    --bloom: #FF4D6D;
    --bloom-dark: #E23256;
    --bloom-pale: #FFE1E7;
    --lilac: #8C6FCB;
    --lilac-pale: #EFE8FB;
    --meadow: #4F9463;
    --meadow-dark: #3D7850;
    --meadow-pale: #E5F3E7;
    --amber: #E8B84E;
    --amber-dark: #B8860B;
    --amber-pale: #FBF2DA;
    --line: #F0DFC5;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'M PLUS Rounded 1c', 'Hiragino Maru Gothic ProN', 'Hiragino Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding: 36px 16px 70px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto; }

  /* header */
  header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--apricot-pale); color: var(--apricot-dark);
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: .03em;
    padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  h1 { font-size: 21px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .lead { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; padding: 0 4px; }

  /* stat cards */
  .stats { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin: 22px 0; }
  .stat {
    flex: 1; background: var(--card); border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 16px 8px; text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 14px rgba(191,140,84,0.14);
  }
  .stat .num { font-size: 25px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--apricot-dark); display: block; }
  .stat .num small { font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 2px; }
  .stat .label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 5px; display: block; }

  /* signature: candle growth chart */
  .chart-card {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: 18px; padding: 18px 16px 14px;
    margin: 0 0 26px; box-shadow: 0 3px 14px rgba(191,140,84,0.14);
  }
  .chart-title { font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 4px; }
  .chart-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .bars { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: space-between; height: 100px; gap: 6px; }
  .bar-col { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; height: 100%; }
  .bar-val { font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--apricot-dark); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .bar { width: 100%; max-width: 26px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--apricot), var(--apricot-dark)); border-radius: 7px 7px 3px 3px; }
  .bar-col.goal .bar { background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bloom), var(--bloom-dark)); }
  .bar-col.goal .bar-val { color: var(--bloom-dark); }
  .bar-day { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 6px; white-space: nowrap; }

  /* point chart (stacked) */
  .pt-bars .bar-val { color: var(--ink); }
  .stack { width: 100%; max-width: 26px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; border-radius: 7px 7px 3px 3px; overflow: hidden; }
  .seg-item { background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--amber), var(--amber-dark)); }
  .seg-walk { background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--meadow), var(--meadow-dark)); }
  .legend { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 18px; margin-top: 14px; }
  .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); }
  .dot { width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; }
  .dot-item { background: var(--amber-dark); }
  .dot-walk { background: var(--meadow); }
  .chart-footnote { font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--muted); text-align: center; margin: 10px 4px 0; }

  /* timeline */
  .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .timeline::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; left: 12px; top: 4px; bottom: 4px;
    width: 3px; background: var(--line); border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .step { position: relative; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .step:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .step-num {
    position: absolute; left: -32px; top: 2px;
    width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--apricot); color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 12.5px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(225,122,27,0.4);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .step.goal .step-num { background: var(--bloom); box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(226,50,86,0.45); }
  .card {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: 16px; padding: 13px 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(191,140,84,0.12);
  }
  .step.goal .card { background: var(--bloom-pale); box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(226,50,86,0.16); }
  .card-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
  .day-tag { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 700; }
  .tier-tag {
    font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--lilac);
    background: var(--lilac-pale); padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .item-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .item-icon { font-size: 22px; line-height: 1; }
  .item-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; }
  .bonus-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: var(--amber-pale); border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 7px 10px; margin: -2px 0 10px;
  }
  .bonus-icon { font-size: 15px; }
  .bonus-text { flex: 1; font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }
  .bonus-pt { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--amber-dark); white-space: nowrap; }
  .card-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
  .cost { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--apricot-dark); }
  .cost small { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; margin-left: 6px; }
  .point-tag {
    font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--amber-dark);
    background: var(--amber-pale); padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 999px;
  }

  /* tier ladder reference */
  .ref {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: 18px; padding: 18px 16px 16px;
    margin: 28px 0 24px; box-shadow: 0 3px 14px rgba(191,140,84,0.14);
  }
  .ref h2 { font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 4px; }
  .ref .ref-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .ladder-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .rung {
    background: var(--apricot-pale); border-radius: 12px; padding: 7px 9px;
    text-align: center; min-width: 50px;
  }
  .rung.goal-rung { background: var(--bloom-pale); }
  .rung .rung-label { display: block; font-size: 10px; color: var(--apricot-dark); font-weight: 700; }
  .rung.goal-rung .rung-label { color: var(--bloom-dark); }
  .rung .rung-pt { display: block; font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 800; margin-top: 2px; }
  .arrow { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
  .ref p.small { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--muted); margin: 6px 2px 0; }

  /* notes */
  .notes {
    background: #FFFAF1; border: 1.5px dashed #E8D2A3; border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 16px 17px; margin-top: 22px;
  }
  .notes p { font-size: 12px; color: #8A7355; margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .notes p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--muted); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <header>
    <span class="kicker">最短ルートガイド</span>
    <h1>🚀 最短ハート交換シミュレーション</h1>
    <p class="lead">連れ歩き（毎日この精霊を選択）とキャンドル購入をこの精霊に集中させた場合の、最速でハートと交換できるルートです。連れ歩きだけで毎日👣+10pt貯まります。</p>
  </header>

  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="num">11<small>日後</small></span>
      <span class="label">ハートと交換できる見込み</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="num">🕯️61<small>本</small></span>
      <span class="label">ここから必要なキャンドル合計</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="chart-card">
    <div class="chart-title">🕯️ 累計キャンドル推移</div>
    <p class="chart-sub">交換のたびに必要本数がどれくらい増えるか一目でわかります</p>
    <div class="bars">
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">4</span>
        <div class="bar" style="height:10px"></div>
        <span class="bar-day">1日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">10</span>
        <div class="bar" style="height:18px"></div>
        <span class="bar-day">2日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">18</span>
        <div class="bar" style="height:30px"></div>
        <span class="bar-day">3日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">36</span>
        <div class="bar" style="height:55px"></div>
        <span class="bar-day">6日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">58</span>
        <div class="bar" style="height:86px"></div>
        <span class="bar-day">10日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col goal">
        <span class="bar-val">61</span>
        <div class="bar" style="height:90px"></div>
        <span class="bar-day">11日目</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="chart-card">
    <div class="chart-title">👣 累計ポイント推移</div>
    <p class="chart-sub">連れ歩き分（🚶）とアイテム交換分（👣）を積み上げた累計ポイントです</p>
    <div class="bars pt-bars">
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">50pt</span>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="seg seg-item" style="height:8px"></div>
          <div class="seg seg-walk" style="height:2px"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="bar-day">1日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">90pt</span>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="seg seg-item" style="height:18px"></div>
          <div class="seg seg-walk" style="height:5px"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="bar-day">2日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">140pt</span>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="seg seg-item" style="height:31px"></div>
          <div class="seg seg-walk" style="height:9px"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="bar-day">3日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">200pt</span>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="seg seg-item" style="height:42px"></div>
          <div class="seg seg-walk" style="height:18px"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="bar-day">6日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">280pt</span>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="seg seg-item" style="height:56px"></div>
          <div class="seg seg-walk" style="height:31px"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="bar-day">10日目</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-col">
        <span class="bar-val">290pt</span>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="seg seg-item" style="height:56px"></div>
          <div class="seg seg-walk" style="height:34px"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="bar-day">11日目</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="legend">
      <span class="legend-item"><i class="dot dot-item"></i>アイテム交換分</span>
      <span class="legend-item"><i class="dot dot-walk"></i>連れ歩き分</span>
    </div>
    <p class="chart-footnote">🎯 10日目で必要な280ptに到達し、11日目に実際の交換が行われる計算です</p>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline">

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <span class="day-tag">1日目</span>
          <span class="tier-tag">第1層</span>
        </div>
        <div class="item-row">
          <span class="item-icon">🪄</span>
          <span class="item-name">魔法①</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bonus-row">
          <span class="bonus-icon">🎁</span>
          <span class="bonus-text">エモートLv1が無料で解放（1日目は確定）</span>
          <span class="bonus-pt">+20pt</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bottom">
          <span class="cost">🕯️ 4本 <small>累計4本</small></span>
          <span class="point-tag">👣+20pt</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <span class="day-tag">2日目</span>
          <span class="tier-tag">第2層</span>
        </div>
        <div class="item-row">
          <span class="item-icon">🪄</span>
          <span class="item-name">魔法②</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bottom">
          <span class="cost">🕯️ 6本 <small>累計10本</small></span>
          <span class="point-tag">👣+30pt</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <span class="day-tag">3日目</span>
          <span class="tier-tag">第3層</span>
        </div>
        <div class="item-row">
          <span class="item-icon">🪄</span>
          <span class="item-name">魔法③</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bottom">
          <span class="cost">🕯️ 8本 <small>累計18本</small></span>
          <span class="point-tag">👣+40pt</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <span class="day-tag">6日目</span>
          <span class="tier-tag">第2層</span>
        </div>
        <div class="item-row">
          <span class="item-icon">🌸</span>
          <span class="item-name">季節アイテム①</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bottom">
          <span class="cost">🕯️ 18本 <small>累計36本</small></span>
          <span class="point-tag">👣+30pt</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">5</div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <span class="day-tag">10日目</span>
          <span class="tier-tag">第3層</span>
        </div>
        <div class="item-row">
          <span class="item-icon">🕺</span>
          <span class="item-name">エモート Lv2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bottom">
          <span class="cost">🕯️ 22本 <small>累計58本</small></span>
          <span class="point-tag">👣+40pt</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step goal">
      <div class="step-num">6</div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <span class="day-tag">11日目</span>
          <span class="tier-tag">第4層</span>
        </div>
        <div class="item-row">
          <span class="item-icon">❤️</span>
          <span class="item-name">ハートと交換 🎉</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bottom">
          <span class="cost">🕯️ 3本 <small>累計61本</small></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="ref">
    <h2>📋 ポイント制のしくみ</h2>
    <p class="ref-sub">2枚目の画像にあったティア構造の早見表です</p>
    <div class="ladder-row">
      <div class="rung"><span class="rung-label">第1層</span><span class="rung-pt">20pt</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
      <div class="rung"><span class="rung-label">第2層</span><span class="rung-pt">40pt</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
      <div class="rung"><span class="rung-label">第3層</span><span class="rung-pt">100pt</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
      <div class="rung"><span class="rung-label">第4層</span><span class="rung-pt">180pt</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
      <div class="rung goal-rung"><span class="rung-label">❤️ハート</span><span class="rung-pt">280pt</span></div>
    </div>
    <p class="small">交換で貯まる👣ポイントが累計でこのラインに届くごとに、次の層のアイテムが解放されていきます。</p>
    <p class="small">🚶 連れ歩きも毎日+10pt貯まるので、アイテムを交換しない日もポイントは少しずつ増えています。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="notes">
    <p>💡 280pt到達に不要なアイテム（季節アイテム②など）は、この最短ルートでは省略しています。見た目も揃えたい場合は、追加で交換してください。</p>
    <p>⚠️ 連れ歩きは1日1体までのため、他の精霊とも分け合う場合はこの日数より遅くなります。キャンドルも他の精霊に使わず、この精霊に全て使った想定の最短見込みです。</p>
  </div>

  <footer>🕯️ Candle Exchange Simulation</footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
